<slide>
	<title>Installing Xdebug</title>
	<subtitle>On Windows</subtitle>

	<list>
		<bullet>Download the .dll for your PHP version from <link href="http://xdebug.org/download.php">http://xdebug.org/download.php</link></bullet>
		<bullet>in php.ini add: %zend_extension_ts=c:\php\xdebug.dll%</bullet>
		<bullet>Tips on finding the correct binary: <link href="http://xdebug.org/find-binary.php"/></bullet>
	</list>
</slide>
